  <p class="sec-body" id="weatherNote" style="margin-bottom:0">Telangana has three seasons: hot summer (March–May), monsoon (June–September) and a pleasant winter (October–February). October to February is ideal — Hyderabad glitters in clear winter light, the Ramappa Temple and Warangal Fort are best explored in cool weather and Bathukamma fills October with flowers.</p>
